description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 MIN BEGINNER FLOOR STRETCHES | growwithjo' from the channel growwithjo.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Stretching is a fun and easy way to boost your body's flexibility and improve your overall physical health! When you stretch, you increase the range of motion in your joints and muscles, which can help to reduce the risk of injury and improve your performance in sports and other physical activities.

In addition to these physical benefits, stretching can also be a great way to relax and de-stress. Taking a few minutes to stretch can help you unwind after a long day, or provide a little pick-me-up during a busy workday.

So why not give stretching a try? Whether you're a seasoned athlete or just looking for a new way to relax and stay healthy, there's something for everyone to enjoy in the wonderful world of stretching! So, go ahead and stretch your way to a happier and healthier you!

All of the stretches will be on the floor today, so grab your mat and get ready to have a comfy stretch!
